data.text:
@DekayArts @Glugglugs really good tipps here, got my second shot 2 days ago and was really happy to have everything i need in arms reach yesterday. 
Today i'm mostly fine, just an itching and swelling around the injection.
@Glugglugs for after that is, kinda get sore and meh feeling for some people after.

@Glugglugs I hope all goes well! just something comfy! you prob will feel lil sore later on, should get you some basic things near you, water, snacks so you don't have to get angry that society really only appreciates refrigerators in the kitchen when you have to walk there
@Glugglugs I got mine yesterday, it was amazingly fast! you have to sit around for 15 minutes afterwards though, charge your phone unless you love staring at strangers in a gymnasium
